caption:
DEADLINE EXTENDED to Aug. 20th!

🚀 Want to get a jumpstart into your professional engineering career? Apply to the Professional Engineers Ontario’s Student Conference (PEO-SC) and connect with industry leaders, innovators, and like-minded students from across Ontario!

📍We are so excited to be hosting PEO-SC 2024 right here at Waterloo! The conference will run from Fri. Oct 4th - Sun. Oct 6th. The conference is typically geared toward upper year student, but all undergradute student are encouraged to apply!

📅Deadline to apply is Tuesday, August 20th

🌟 Don’t miss out on this opportunity to level up your skills and expand your network. Apply now and be part of the future! 🔗 https://bit.ly/PEO-SC24Apps

caption:
Calling all incoming first years! 😎 Get ready for an unforgettable experience at our Third Annual Aviation Intro Day this September! Join the University of Waterloo Aviation Society for a day packed with games, challenges, and amazing prizes! 🏆

Don’t miss out—sign up now using the link in our bio!

📅 Intro Day Date: Sunday, September 8th, 11:30 AM - 5:30 PM

Tag a fellow first year below for a chance to win a special Prize during our closing ceremonies! Eligible programs include Geography and Aviation Science, Aviation, and GEM Aviation Specialization.

See you there! ✈️✈️

caption: TaqwaCon 2.0 is coming back 🕌✨ Join us for a transformative 2-Day Islamic Convention on October 12-13, 2024, at the University of Waterloo. This Taqwa-centred convention will bring Muslims from around Ontario for two action packed days. 🙌🌟 Theme: TAQWA📚 Immerse in academic lectures🗣️ Engage with exceptional speakers🤝 Build a vibrant community🎉 Enjoy exciting entertainmentTaqwa, the core theme, embodies the consciousness of Allah’s presence, nurturing righteousness and moral integrity while steering clear of sinful actions. Let’s come together for an inspiring journey of growth and unity. Save the date and become a part of this transformative experience! 💫
